      <title>印度法院允许陷入困境的 Byju’s 召开股东大会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/india-court-allows-embattled-byju-s-to-hold-shareholder-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度在线辅导公司 Byju’s 将于 3 月 29 日按计划召开股东大会，此前该公司法院拒绝了一些投资者推迟会议的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/india-court-allows-embattled-byju-s-to-hold-shareholder-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:32:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者在财报期间青睐日本，避开中国和印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/investors-shun-china-and-india-reward-japan-as-earnings-season-winds-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着亚太地区的财报季稍事休息，从投资者获得收益的情况来看，他们显然更青睐日本公司的股票，而回避香港、中国和印度的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/investors-shun-china-and-india-reward-japan-as-earnings-season-winds-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲运营商 Telecel 收购 MTN 资产作为 IPO 推动的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/african-operator-telecel-snaps-up-mtn-assets-as-part-of-ipo-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Telecel Group 已从非洲最大的无线公司 MTN Group Ltd. 手中收购了两家西非子公司，以在三年内首次公开募股之前扩大业务规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/african-operator-telecel-snaps-up-mtn-assets-as-part-of-ipo-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
