      <title>是德科技出价 12 亿英镑收购思博伦，超越 Viavi</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/keysight-bids-1-2-billion-for-spirent-overtaking-viavi-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[是德科技向陷入困境的英国电信网络测试公司思博伦通信公司提出了报价，超过了 Viavi Solutions Inc. 此前对这家英国公司的报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/keysight-bids-1-2-billion-for-spirent-overtaking-viavi-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
