      <title>昂贵的电动汽车押注首次亮相，小米80亿美元的涨势岌岌可危</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/smartphone-billionaire-begins-assault-on-tesla-and-200-billion-ev-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，中国智能手机巨头小米推出首款电动汽车，试图打入一个陌生且竞争激烈的市场，这家中国智能手机巨头的 80 亿美元股价上涨面临着关键考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/smartphone-billionaire-begins-assault-on-tesla-and-200-billion-ev-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
